Short:    pitch shifter source in ansi c
Uploader: PeterC@nym.alias.net
Author:   Peter Capasso
Type:     dev/src

This is source in C for a working pitch shifter which uses the
overlap add (doppler) method of shifting.  I could not find
source anywhere for doing this.  Here it is.  Short, simple,
and free.

Now there is no excuse for not putting a pitch shifter in all
audio software.  :-)
